content:
...(examining you) {短暂停}
Oh, no matter - you must have changed your attire.
You appear to be, {短暂停} quite well-mannered.

There's no doubt about it,
you've undergone quite a transformation! {开心}
It seems you've mastered the ritual of living joyfully.

That outfit of yours—
while perhaps not ideal for martial arts practice,
it's absolutely gor~geous!
